Cell.Text: I am Knight-Paladin Gelebor. Welcome to the Great Chantry of Auri-El.
Auriel, Auri-El, Alkosh, Akatosh... so many different names for the sovereign of the snow elves.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic01: This cave is a temple to Auriel?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A856 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: I prefer snow elf. The name "Falmer" usually holds a negative meaning to most travellers. | Those twisted creatures you call Falmer, I call the Betrayed.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic02: Snow elves? You're a Falmer?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A854 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: For the thousands of years I've served as the Chantry's sentinel, there hasn't been a single visitor here for any other reason. | They request Auriel's Bow, and I request their assistance. It's been repeated so many times, I can't imagine it any other way.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic04a: How did you know?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A853 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:builds Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: The kinship between us gone. I don't understand what he's become, but he's no longer the brother I once knew. | It was the Betrayed... they did something to him, I just don't know why Auri-El would allow this to happen.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborSecondBranchTopic: Kill your brother, why?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A850 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: The Chantry was a place of peaceful worship. I lead a small group of paladins, but we were no match for the Betrayed's sheer numbers. | They slaughtered everyone and stormed the Inner Sanctum where I believe they corrupted Vyrthur.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborSecondBranchTopic01: Didn't you fight back?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A84F - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: He's alive. I've seen him. | But something's wrong. He never looks as though he's in pain or under duress. He just... stands there and watches, as though waiting.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborSecondBranchTopic02: You don't even know if he's alive.

Node.ToolTip:
0100A84E - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:builds Date:4/4/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: Leaving the wayshrines unguarded would be violating my sacred duty as a Knight-Paladin of Auriel. | And an assault on the Betrayed guarding the Inner Sanctum would only end with my death.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborSecondBranchTopic03: Have you tried getting into the Inner Sanctum?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A852 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: [S] I need you to kill Arch-Curate Vyrthur... my bother.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic04b: What type of assistance do you need?

Node.ToolTip:
0100A851 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:4/3/2012 File:DLC01.esm

Cell.Text: Absolutely. You could turn around and travel back from wherever you started empty handed, or you could assist me.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic04c: Do I have a choice?

Cell.Text: Of course. You're here for Auriel's Bow. Why else would you be here? | I can help you get it, but first I must have your assistance.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborIntroBranchTopic03: I imagine you know why we're here.

Cell.Text: They swept into the Chantry without warning and began killing everyone without pause.

Node.Caption: DLC1VQ07GeleborSecondBranchTopic01a: What exactly did the Betrayed do?
